            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-600">✓</span>
              <span>灵活套餐，按需购买</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-600">✓</span>
              <span>适合轻中度使用需求</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">🔧 适用场景：</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
